#. type: Title ====
#: UG9/en/linstor-administration.adoc:3311
#, no-wrap
msgid "Health Checking"
msgstr ""

#. type: Table
#: UG9/en/linstor-administration.adoc:3317
msgid ""
"The LINSTOR-Controller also provides a `/health` HTTP path that will simply "
